TRANSLATION :
Forwarded from SIGNAL Automobile blogger Eric Davidych talked about his work as an advisor to the general director of the Moskvich plant. In the video, which quickly gained hundreds of thousands of views, he talks about how to save the plant and the workforce, how much the new car will cost, etc.  
  
Davidych emphasizes that the stimulation of own automobile industry is a matter of national security, because the cars used in cabs, ambulances and other areas will become too expensive to maintain because of the sanctions. Due to logistics problems and sanctions, it will be more and more difficult to service them. Also in the video blogger compared the prices of Chinese and Russian cars.   YouTube Moskvich. The beginning ..... The history of the Moskvich plant, answers to the main questions.  
 
In this film you will get acquainted with the long history of the plant, with the legendary Moskvich, which in its time was the dream of every Soviet citizen.  
The plant employees will tell about their experiences, and you, dear friends, will finally see the car, which in our reality is sold under the Moskvich brand and hopefully you will understand the profound task, which this car carries on its shoulders.
